Text:
Thanks much. A very nice 3+ hour tape from top artists. Well worthy addition to anyone's collection. I converted it to MP3 and put it on my car's MP3 player. I've been seeding ever since downloading.
Anxious to hear more of your tapes.

@redhotcooljazz Thanks for the comment, glad to hear you enjoyed it. I don't have much free time these days, so updates will be rather spaced out, but they are coming. I believe I will be doing a classical 4 track for my next upload. I am currently in the process of transferring all my 2-tracks from the 1950's.
